                <h1>Fleetwood Mac: The Iconic Rock Band</h1>
                <p>Fleetwood Mac is a legendary British-American rock band formed in 1967. Known for their unique blend of rock, pop, and blues, the group's most iconic lineup included Lindsey Buckingham, Stevie Nicks, Christine McVie, John McVie, and Mick Fleetwood. Their album "Rumours" remains one of the best-selling records in history.</p>
